While speaking to Shelley Wade of 94.7 The Block, the television host, who is reportedly expecting his eighth and ninth child with two different women, was asked whether he would consider marrying again. "I've failed miserably so many times at monogamy and relationships. But God ain't done with me. We're gonna figure it out." Nick Cannon via 94.7 The Block. On what the "deciding factor" would be for marriage, he responded. "I've probably had a few mid-life crises, (but) I'm liking the man that I'm growing into."